      "description": "This used car is in good condition. The exterior has minor scratches and light wear consistent with normal use, but no significant dents or rust, and the paint is largely intact with minimal fading. The interior shows some light wear on the upholstery but remains clean and functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately.",
